incorporateType(Type) - Method in class uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.Resolver
The given type is incorporated into the resolver, in a fashion dictated by the class of that type, as follows: Class as per Resolver.incorporateTypeParameters(GenericDeclaration). ParameterizedType as per Resolver.captureTypeArguments(ParameterizedType). GenericArrayType as per Resolver.incorporateType(Type) invoked for it's component type. IntersectionType as per Resolver.incorporateType(Type) invoked for each member. WildcardType as per Resolver.inferOverWildcardType(WildcardType).
